data.description: Largest property in Garden Villas for sale at this time. Over one acre-1.3 to be exact- snap shot of dimensions posted in attachments.  2 story with the upstairs set up as all the primary bedroom, 32ft x 32ft, divide if needed or keep as primary oasis.  All other bedrooms down. Floors down were said to be large slate tiles per property owner. Upstairs is carpet. Walk in shower down. Back yard cleared and ready to be transformed by your imagination.  Pool was covered with sand by seller, outline can be seen from upstairs. Fireplace on each level. Come check it out.
